" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Heroes of the High Court pg. 3</i></a><br /><b>Requirement(s)</b> Associated with the court of the Imperial Palace in Cheliax<br />Your experience working with devils has given you nerves of steel. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Will saves to resist fear effects created by outsiders.<br /><br /></span>
