            <span id="MainContent_DataListTypes_LabelType_87"><h2 class="title"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Knowing the Enemy [<a href="TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Knowing the Enemy" style="font-color: white">Link</a>]</h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy8x64?Pathfinder-Roleplaying-Game-Ultimate-Campaign
