		<td>
            <span id="MainContent_DataListTypes_LabelType_98"><h2 class="title"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Mercenary [<a href="TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Mercenary" style="font-color: white">Link</a>]</h2><b>Source</b> <a href="http://paizo.com/products/btpy8x64?Pathfinder-Roleplaying-Game-Ultimate-Campaign
" target="_blank" class="external-link"><i>Ultimate Campaign pg. 60</i></a><br /> For everything there is a price, and you are a negotiator at heart. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Diplomacy, Intimidate, and Sense Motive checks made while negotiating payment for a quest or a service that you provide.<br /><br /></span>
